<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        .header { color: #334155; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; }
        .reason-box { background-color: #fff7ed; border-left: 4px solid #f97316; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .button { background-color: #334155; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">Update needed for your application</div>
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for applying to Bleefy. Upon reviewing your profile, our team found that we need some adjustments before we can grant you full marketplace access.</p>
        
        <div class="reason-box">
            <strong style="color: #c2410c;">Reason for this update:</strong><br/>
            {{reason}}
        </div>
        
        <p>Please update your onboarding details and resubmit for verification. We are looking forward to having you on the platform!</p>
        
        <a href="{{onboardingUrl}}" class="button">Update My Profile</a>
        
        <div class="footer">
            If you believe this was a mistake, please reply to this email to chat with our support team.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>